name: Late to Area 51 (Wolverine Soft)
description:
You arrived a day late to Area 51 raid. Will you be able to rescue the aliens that have been left behind? Play to find out!

Made by Seyhyun Yang, Michael Tilbury, Nathan Gualtieri, Blake Webb, and Dilan Huang for WolverineSoft's 2019 Pumpkin Game Jam.
